Interface com.chimu.kernel.streams.Generator

public interface Generator
extends Function0Arg, Enumeration
A Generator produces objects either one at a time or in collections.

Compatibility: #next and #nextElement are both compatibility synonyms for #nextValue, #hasMoreElements is always true.

Method Index

currentValue()
Return the current value of the generator.
hasMoreElements()
This will always return true
nextElement()
nextValue()
Generate and return a new value for the generator
value()
This is just to support using a Generator as a Function0Arg, Generator clients should call "nextValue" (the synonym) instead.
